80\\u0099t even make it on to the podium.\", \"from\": 215, \"to\": 352, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 227, \"end\": 230, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LBC\", \"score\": 0.9999999993674464, \"rank\": 6.323395770958701e-10, \"text\": \"LBC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LBC\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her routine\", \"from\": 259, \"to\": 270}, {\"ngram\": \"the world champion\", \"from\": 272, \"to\": 290}, {\"ngram\": \"the podium\", \"from\": 341, \"to\": 351}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cGoing in to it, I felt like maybe I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099ll finish fifth, maybe I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099ll miss out on the medals \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0093 you have all of those worries and all of the negative thoughts going through your brain\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d, she said.\", \"from\": 354, \"to\": 553, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"finish\", \"from\": 398, \"to\": 404}, {\"ngram\": \"the medals\", \"from\": 437, \"to\": 447}, {\"ngram\": \"those worries\", \"from\": 468, \"to\": 481}, {\"ngram\": \"the negative thoughts\", \"from\": 493, \"to\": 514}, {\"ngram\": \"your brain\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d\", \"from\": 529, \"to\": 542}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cMy brain is so annoying sometimes, I just have to tell it to shut up\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d.\", \"from\": 554, \"to\": 629, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cMy brain\", \"from\": 554, \"to\": 565}, {\"ngram\": \"up\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d.\", \"from\": 623, \"to\": 629}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 33-year-old, who took silver in Rio 2016 and bronze in Tokyo 2020, said she \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009crefocused\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d and \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009ctried to stay calm in the moment\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d, to get her through the show-stopping 10-skill routine which saw her top the leaderboard.\", \"from\": 631, \"to\": 859, \"enti