ela_Carini\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angela_Carini\"}, {\"begin\": 1037, \"end\": 1040, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"score\": 0.9996309951463361, \"rank\": 0.0003691307230412651, \"text\": \"IBA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\"}, {\"begin\": 1067, \"end\": 1074, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"score\": 0.9999950660843597, \"rank\": 3.338396863749346e-06, \"text\": \"Algeria\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Olympic medal table\", \"from\": 900, \"to\": 919}, {\"ngram\": \"trampolining\", \"from\": 926, \"to\": 938}, {\"ngram\": \"golds\", \"from\": 963, \"to\": 968}, {\"ngram\": \"prize money\", \"from\": 1021, \"to\": 1032}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic defeat\", \"from\": 1048, \"to\": 1062}, {\"ngram\": \"a mistake\", \"from\": 1112, \"to\": 1121}, {\"ngram\": \"her routine\", \"from\": 1137, \"to\": 1148}, {\"ngram\": \"air\", \"from\": 1166, \"to\": 1169}, {\"ngram\": \"her final trick\", \"from\": 1174, \"to\": 1189}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She also admitted she had forgotten there was still an athlete left to compete after her, so prematurely celebrated as though she had won gold.\", \"from\": 1241, \"to\": 1384, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an athlete\", \"from\": 1293, \"to\": 1303}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 1379, \"to\": 1383}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI reacted as if I had already won the gold, and then I remembered there was another person to go.\", \"from\": 1386, \"to\": 1486, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI\", \"from\": 1386, \"to\": 1390}, {\"ngram\": \"the gold\", \"from\": 1423, \"to\": 1431}, {\"ngram\": \"another person\", \"from\": 1465, \"to\": 1479}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I thought \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0098at least I know what it\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s like to feel like an Olympic champion, even if it\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s taken away from me.\", \"from\": 1487, \"to\": 1601, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0098at\", \"from\": 1497, \"to\": 1502}, {\"ngram\": \"it\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 1521, \"to\": 1527}, {\"ngram\": \"an Olympic champion\", \"from\": 1546, \"to\": 1565}, {\"ngram\": \"it\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 1575, \"to\": 1581}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But it wasn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t, so we\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099re all good.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Jess Thom, Team GB\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s lead psychologist told LBC \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cit\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s not abnormal\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d for athletes to feel anxious.\", \"from\": 1602, \"to\": 1749, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1644, \"end\": 1653, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jess_Thom\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jess Thom\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jess_Thom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jess_Thom\"}, {\"begin\": 1690, \"end\": 1693, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LBC\", \"score\": 0.9999999993674464, \"rank\": 6.323395770958701e-10, \"text\": \"LBC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LBC\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Team GB\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 1654, \"to\": 1665}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 1723, \"to\": 1731}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She told Matthew Wright: \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cOlympians have similar thoughts and feelings to every day people \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0093 when they\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099re competing they\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099re very good at staying in the moment and being present, but it\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s not abnormal to hear athletes before they get to the start line talking about feeling anxious, and feeling like things could go wrong.\", \"from\": 1751, \"to\": 2082, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1760, \"end\": 1774, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matthew_Wright_(basketball)\", \"score\": 0.8023344496027278, \"rank\": 0.18001818783064374, \"text\": \"Matthew Wright\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matthew_Wright_(basketball)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matthew_Wright_(basketball)\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cOlympians\", \"from\": 1776, \"to\": 1788}, {\"ngram\": \"similar thoughts\", \"from\": 1794, \"to\": 1810}, {\"ngram\": \"feelings\", \"from\": 1815, \"to\": 1823}, {\"ngram\": \"every day\", \"from\": 1827, \"to\": 1836}, {\"ngram\": \"the moment\", \"from\": 1907, \"to\": 1917}, {\"ngram\": \"it\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 1941, \"to\": 1947}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 1969, \"to\": 1977}, {\"ngram\": \"the start line\", \"from\": 1997, \"to\": 2011}, {\"ngram\": \"things\", \"from\": 2060, \"to\": 2066}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cThese guys are pros at managing the pressure, they work so hard year on year to prepare for that moment, so they have a really clear idea of what they\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099re there to do and what success looks like.\", \"from\": 2084, \"to\": 2283, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cThese guys\", \"from\": 2084, \"to\": 2097}, {\"ngram\": \"pros\", \"from\": 2102, \"to\": 2106}, {\"ngram\": \"the pressure\", \"from\": 2119, \"to\": 2131}, {\"ngram\": \"year\", \"from\": 2159, \"to\": 2163}, {\"ngram\": \"that moment\", \"from\": 2179, \"to\": 2190}, {\"ngram\": \"a really clear idea\", \"from\": 2205, \"to\": 2224}, {\"ngram\": \"what they\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099re\", \"from\": 2228, \"to\": 2242}, {\"ngram\": \"what success\", \"from\": 2259, \"to\": 2271}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They have amazing strategies to manage those unhelpful thoughts and feelings that will inevitably show up\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d, she said.\", \"from\": 2284, \"to\": 2403, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"amazing strategies\", \"from\": 2294, \"to\": 2312}, {\"ngram\": \"those unhelpful thoughts\", \"from\": 2323, \"to\": 2347}, {\"ngram\": \"feelings\", \"from\": 2352, \"to\": 2360}, {\"ngram\": \"up\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d\", \"from\": 2387, \"to\": 2392}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Having achieved the title of World champion and Olympic champion, Page now has her sights set on the circus.\", \"from\": 2405, \"to\": 2513, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the title\", \"from\": 2421, \"to\": 2430}, {\"ngram\": \"World champion\", \"from\": 2434, \"to\": 2448}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic champion\", \"from\": 2453, \"to\": 2469}, {\"ngram\": \"Page\", \"from\": 2471, \"to\": 2475}, {\"ngram\": \"her sights\", \"from\": 2484, \"to\": 2494}, {\"ngram\": \"the circus\", \"from\": 2502, \"to\": 2512}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She told LBC: \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099m hoping that Cirque du Soleil might want me at some point before I get too old.\", \"from\": 2515, \"to\": 2616, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2524, \"end\": 2527, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LBC\", \"score\": 0.9999999993674464, \"rank\": 6.323395770958701e-10, \"text\": \"LBC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LBC\"}, {\"begin\": 2550, \"end\": 2566, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cirque_du_Soleil\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Cirque du Soleil\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cirque_du_Soleil\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cirque_du_Soleil\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099m\", \"from\": 2529, \"to\": 2537}, {\"ngram\": \"some point\", \"from\": 2584, \"to\": 2594}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099d love to have that experience and perform in front of a crowd in a different way \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0093 I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099ve dreamed about that for a really long time so I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099d love to have the opportunity to do it\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d.\", \"from\": 2617, \"to\": 2806, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099d\", \"from\": 2617, \"to\": 2622}, {\"ngram\": \"that experience\", \"from\": 2636, \"to\": 2651}, {\"ngram\": \"front\", \"from\": 2667, \"to\": 2672}, {\"ngram\": \"a crowd\", \"from\": 2676, \"to\": 2683}, {\"ngram\": \"a different way\", \"from\": 2687, \"to\": 2702}, {\"ngram\": \"a really long time\", \"from\": 2737, \"to\": 2755}, {\"ngram\": \"I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099d\", \"from\": 2759, \"to\": 2764}, {\"ngram\": \"the opportunity\", \"from\": 2778, \"to\": 2793}, {\"ngram\": \"it\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d.\", \"from\": 2800, \"to\": 2806}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She also did not rule out competing in the LA games in 2028 and Brisbane in 2032, and said she hoped Cirque de Soleil would let her return to the circus after the Olympics.\", \"from\": 2808, \"to\": 2980, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2909, \"end\": 2925, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cirque_du_Soleil\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Cirque de Soleil\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cirque_du_Soleil\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cirque_du_Soleil\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the LA games\", \"from\": 2847, \"to\": 2859}, {\"ngram\": \"the circus\", \"from\": 2950, \"to\": 2960}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 2967, \"to\": 2979}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The use of the Ajax vehicle was halted for two weeks to allow an investigation to be